    "caveat": "Goncalves' pooled 5v5 iso of -0.076 comes from a depth-line role over 1729 min. Promotion to L2 with Guentzel-Point means tougher opposition (other teams' L1) — historical L4-to-L2 promotions show an iso compression of 30-50% on per-60 metrics. The +0.5 xG/g number is the pre-compression upper bound; realistic is closer to half that."
  },
